Stage 2: PLANNER2 (Answer Generation)
File: planner2_stage.py:37-150

Purpose: Generate answers using LLM with retrieved context

Key Operations:

Wait for Parallel Tasks (lines 59-77):
Waits for parallel retrieval if started by compact planner
Waits for web search results
Waits for Knowledge Graph NLQ processing
Preprocessing (line 80):
Uses version-specific preprocessors (PREPROCESSORS)
Constructs prompt with retrieved documents
Formats context for LLM
LLM Call with Streaming (lines 128-135):
